=head1 DESCRIPTION

Information for sorting a list of domains.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Name => Str

Field to be used for sorting the list of domains. It can be either the
name or the expiration for a domain. Note that if C<filterCondition> is
used in the same ListDomains
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/Route53/latest/APIReference/API_domains__ListDomains.html)
call, the field used for sorting has to be the same as the field used
for filtering.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> SortOrder => Str

The sort order for a list of domains. Either ascending (ASC) or
descending (DES).



